### 1. List all atomic modeling claims made by the reference system model

1. The model imports ScalarValues::Real.
2. The model imports ISQ::*.

6. Defines part Vehicle.
7. Vehicle has attribute mass of type MassValue.
8. Vehicle has attribute fuelLevel of type Real.
9. Vehicle has attribute fuelTankCapacity of type Real.
10. Defines part Engine.
11. Engine has port drivePwrPort of type DrivePwrPort.
12. Engine performs action 'generate torque' of type 'Generate Torque'.
13. Defines part Transmission.
14. Transmission has port clutchPort of type ClutchPort.
15. Defines port DrivePwrPort.
16. Defines port ClutchPort.
17. Defines interface EngineToTransmissionInterface.
18. EngineToTransmissionInterface has end drivePwrPort of type DrivePwrPort.
19. EngineToTransmissionInterface has end clutchPort of type ClutchPort.
20. Defines action 'Generate Torque'.

#### Package 'Vehicle Usages'
21. Publicly imports 'Vehicle Definitions'::*.
22. Defines action 'provide power'.
23. 'provide power' action includes sub-action 'generate torque'.
24. Defines part vehicle1_c1 of type Vehicle.
25. vehicle1_c1 has attribute mass = 2000 [kg].
26. vehicle1_c1 performs 'provide power'.
27. vehicle1_c1 has part engine_v1 of type Engine.
28. engine_v1 has port drivePwrPort.
29. engine_v1 performs 'provide power'.'generate torque' mapped to 'generate torque'.
30. vehicle1_c1 has part transmission of type Transmission.
31. transmission has port clutchPort.
32. vehicle1_c1 has interface engineToTransmission of type EngineToTransmissionInterface.
33. engineToTransmission connects engine_v1.drivePwrPort to transmission.clutchPort.
34. Defines part vehicle1_c2 of type Vehicle.
35. vehicle1_c2 has attribute mass = 2500 [kg].

#### Package 'Vehicle Requirements'
36. Publicly imports 'Vehicle Definitions'::*.
37. Defines requirement MassLimitationRequirement (id '1').
38. MassLimitationRequirement has attribute massActual of type MassValue.
39. MassLimitationRequirement has attribute massReqd of type MassValue.
40. MassLimitationRequirement has constraint: massActual <= massReqd.
41. Defines requirement ReliabilityRequirement (id '2').
42. Defines requirement vehicleMass1 (id '1.1') of type MassLimitationRequirement.
43. vehicleMass1 has subject vehicle of type Vehicle.
44. vehicleMass1 has attribute massActual = vehicle.mass.
45. vehicleMass1 has attribute massReqd = 2000 [kg].
46. vehicleMass1 has assumed constraint fuelConstraint: vehicle.fuelLevel >= vehicle.fuelTankCapacity.
47. Defines requirement vehicleMass2 (id '2.1') of type MassLimitationRequirement.
48. vehicleMass2 has subject vehicle of type Vehicle.
49. vehicleMass2 has attribute massActual = vehicle.mass.
50. vehicleMass2 has attribute massReqd = 2500 [kg].
51. vehicleMass2 has assumed constraint fuelConstraint: vehicle.fuelLevel == 0.0.
52. Defines requirement vehicleReliability2 (id '2.2') of type ReliabilityRequirement.
53. vehicleReliability2 has subject vehicle of type Vehicle.
54. Defines requirement drivePowerInterface (id '3.1').
55. drivePowerInterface has subject drivePwrPort of type DrivePwrPort.
56. Defines requirement torqueGeneration (id '3.2').
57. torqueGeneration has subject generateTorque of type 'Generate Torque'.

#### Specification Contexts
58. Defines part 'vehicle1_c1 Specification Context'.
59. 'vehicle1_c1 Specification Context' imports 'vehicle1-c1 Specification'::* privately.
60. 'vehicle1_c1 Specification Context' imports 'engine-v1 Specification'::* privately.
61. Defines requirement 'vehicle1-c1 Specification'.
62. 'vehicle1-c1 Specification' has subject vehicle of type Vehicle.
63. 'vehicle1-c1 Specification' references vehicleMass1.
64. Defines requirement 'engine-v1 Specification'.
65. 'engine-v1 Specification' has subject engine of type Engine.
66. 'engine-v1 Specification' requires torqueGeneration, with in: generateTorque = engine.'generate torque'.
67. 'engine-v1 Specification' requires drivePowerInterface, with in: drivePwrPort = engine.drivePwrPort.
68. 'vehicle1_c1 Specification Context' satisfies 'vehicle1-c1 Specification' by vehicle1_c1.
69. 'vehicle1_c1 Specification Context' satisfies 'engine-v1 Specification' by vehicle1_c1.engine_v1.
70. Defines part 'vehicle1_c2 Specification Context'.
71. 'vehicle1_c2 Specification Context' imports 'vehicle1-c2 Specification'::* privately.
72. Defines requirement 'vehicle1-c2 Specification'.
73. 'vehicle1-c2 Specification' has subject vehicle of type Vehicle.
